  "title": "Driver & Plant Nurturer | Class 3 | Bedok | 9755",
  "description": "<p><strong>Role: Driver cum Plant Nurturer x 2 Headcount</strong></p><p><strong>5.5 Days Per Week | Sunday OFF | 8am-5pm (Mon to Fri) | 8am to 12pm (Sat)</strong></p><p><strong>Location: Bedok</strong></p><p><strong>Basic Salary: SGD $2,300 - $2,400 + OT</strong></p><p><strong>Entitled to Medical Benefits & Bonus</strong></p><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ol><li><strong>Class 3 driving license, driving 10 footer lorry, manual type, vehicle unable to drive back.</strong></li><li><strong>Min 2 years of driving experience is required for this role</strong></li></ol><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Adhere to assigned schedule and ensure work tasks are completed on time.</li><li>Transporting workers and goods to sites.</li><li>Collecting and disposing of rubbish from work sites.</li><li>Safely securing heavy loads and large goods for transport.</li><li>Organizing the most efficient route from pickup point to drop off point.</li><li>Organizing multiple drop-offs and deliveries in each working day.</li><li>Support landscape and hydroculture maintenance work.</li><li>Upkeep assigned company vehicle: routine checking of engine; & general cleanliness.</li><li>Ensuring vehicles are mechanically sound and legally roadworthy.</li><li>Immediately complete and submit accident reports (e.g., injuries) to your manager.</li><li>Supervising and assisting with the loading and unloading of deliveries into the lorry.</li><li>Complying with all LTA and in-house regulations and rule.</li><li>Other duties and responsibilities as assigned.</li></ul><p>Tai Jia Seng Reg No: R26159755<br />The Supreme Hr Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
